<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT9">
<l>kuṟaikoṇṭu nāṉmukaṉ kuṇṭikainīr peytu</l>
<l>maṟaikoṇṭa mantirattāl vāḻtti kaṟaikoṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṇṭattāṉ ceṉṉimē lēṟak kaḻuviṉā</l>
<l>ṉaṇṭattāṉ cēvaṭiyai yāṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having had [his] wants fulfilled, the four-faced [Brahmā] poured water</l>
<l rend="indent">from the pitcher on that day</l>
<l>[and] praising [Him] with Vedic mantras,</l>
<l>[he] washed the red feet of the Lord of the Universe so that [the water] entered</l>
<l>the head of [Śiva] with a stained throat.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
